{"tid":978111,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打絲打2019年3月19號前要驗車？","createTime":"2019-01-11T15:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T06:14:08.000Z","uid":230742,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fc83359da18bafe441cbce3eca9220b7a4c7fd59","tid":978111,"uid":230742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T15:55:08.000Z","msg":"請問有無巴絲2019年3月19號前要安排驗車？<br />\n<br />\n話說我上年P牌買左架錢七，無幾耐見網上驗車優惠（團購券）諗住買埋<br />\n點知買完券，轉頭忍唔住買左架新車，變相唔洗咁快驗車住<br />\n希望睇下會唔會有巴絲有興趣幫手要左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原先個優惠價$900 包：<br />\n1. 政府驗車前全面檢測 (價值 $1200)<br />\n2. 免費代交政府指定驗車中心檢驗（已包政府驗車費$585）<br />\n3. 全人手洗車及吸塵服務 (價值 $280)<br />\n4. 另外到時驗車即場可以 + $1 更換汽車機油（加德士HAVOLINE-5W40全合成機油4公升，不包油隔及風隔。我新牌仔唔知邊隻好，到時請自行決定會唔會加D錢換其他牌子<br />\n<br />\n代辨驗車的車房地點：<br />\n挑戰者汽車維修中心（觀塘興業街16-18號地下 ）<br />\n電話：2341 1868 ; 營業時間：(星期一至五) 8:00am-7:00pm, (星期六) 9:00am-6:00pm，星期日及勞工假期休息<br />\n<br />\n請注意：<br />\n1. 優惠券有效日期至2019年3月19日<br />\n2. 法例規定，如車牌將於4個月內屆滿，就可安排驗車(即是2019年7月18日之前到期驗車的話，就可以用呢張券)<br />\n3. 最少3天前致電23411868預約驗車<br />\n4. 優惠只適用於一般私家車 (不限排氣量cc)，不適用於特別車款、超跑及商用車<br />\n<br />\n張優惠券需要印出黎，驗車時比車房就可以<br />\n如家中唔方便列印文件，我可以印左之後再郵寄給你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者發電子版文件給你自己列印亦可，謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望轉讓價錢：$800，如有興趣的話請tg或者pm我<br />\n（tg：waiyau）<br />\n<br />\n政府驗車費都要$585，$800包埋check車同洗車吸塵<br />\n我估...應該算好平.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 麻煩大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個係之前團購券個網，請入去睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.deals.yahoo.com/hong-kong/offer/history/1236950\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.deals.yahoo.com%2Fhong-kong%2Foffer%2Fhistory%2F1236950&d=qx6SGytK11ti6wVBFdTZ3smB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=83f563e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.deals.yahoo.com/hong-kong/offer/history/1236950</a>"},{"pid":"c8dcab89ae07f8007b1d6f097d46322a68e8ada5","tid":978111,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T19:14:02.000Z","msg":"挑戰者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec3d97627b7baea77ad78d09af962a19b4f4349","tid":978111,"uid":230742,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c8dcab89ae07f8007b1d6f097d46322a68e8ada5","tid":978111,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T19:14:02.000Z","msg":"挑戰者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T19:19:34.000Z","msg":"巴打，間野咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係P仔絲，咩都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eecfd94e3a7d362a27376adbf200308e88e80aa","tid":978111,"uid":13556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T19:22:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驗車比呢d洗車屋搞？"},{"pid":"58b28b7de61b86181092ab272369073b435b863a","tid":978111,"uid":230742,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8eecfd94e3a7d362a27376adbf200308e88e80aa","tid":978111,"uid":13556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T19